name: YOU USE TIME : TIME USE YOU
description:
Tale of Perseverance I: Time is a wild beast, it consumes anything in its path. Time is also manipulative and can put you to sleep if you don't catch it doing it to you. One should be brave and cunning enough to tame it. If one manage to hold time by their side, they will have control over their destiny.
-
"It's either you use your time, or time will use you" I've enough be used by time for its bidding, it's time to do something with my time.
